explanation: [0-0] The scene is a room decorated with gray brick walls. A man with curly black hair, wearing a black suit, black tie, and sunglasses, is standing in the center of the frame. His hands are clasped in front of him, and there is a large cardboard box to his right. The ceiling is white.

[0-9] A hand holding a few euro banknotes hands the money to him. The man takes the banknotes and slowly opens the lid of the cardboard box. Inside the box is a dimly lit space, and as the lid opens, a black cat can be seen. The light inside the box brightens, revealing a green light effect, and another calico cat can be seen. The room is furnished with a cartoon-patterned mattress, cat food, and water bowls. The light inside the box continuously changes color, from green to purple, then to blue, and then to red. Several kittens are moving freely around the room, creating a dynamic scene.
